Package com.zebra.sdk.common.card.graphics.barcode.enumerations

Enumerations used within card printer barcode generation

See: Description

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BaselinePosition
    Enumeration for the alignment of bars when the heights are not uniform.
    ChecksumMode
    Enumeration type for the checksum policy.
    Code128CharacterSet
    Specifies the character set to use in the Code 128 symbology.
    ErrorCorrectionLevel
    Enumeration for the four QR code error correction levels.
    HumanReadablePlacement
    Enumeration for placement of the human readable portion of a barcode.
    LogicalHeight
    Enumeration for retrieving the Postnet bar height.
    Rotation
    Specifies the CW rotation of the barcode.
    SymbolShape
    Enumeration for the data matrix symbol shape hint.
